Weâve partnered with many providers in your area. Find one who meets your needs using the search tool below. You can search by name, specialty or location.

Search for many different types of providers, like:

Primary care providers (PCP)

Specialists

Hospitals and facilities

Behavioral health providers (mental health and substance abuse)

Labs (to get blood tests)

Pharmacies

Vision care providers

Long-term care providers

Search now

You can download a provider directory to see all providers in your service area. To have a directory mailed to you at no cost, call Member Services. You can find the number for your plan on the Contact Us page.
